WEBVTT

00:02.381 --> 00:05.695
Okay, Sammy,
let's try this again.

00:07.352 --> 00:08.767
Aaaah.

00:10.182 --> 00:11.563
Uh, uh...

00:12.598 --> 00:14.704
Eeuh, uh, uh...

00:15.877 --> 00:18.880
Ash-- aah...asshole.
[ Laughs ]

00:18.915 --> 00:22.091
[ Laughter ]Oh, this is very productive.

00:22.125 --> 00:23.954
Monty, you know
as well as I do

00:23.989 --> 00:26.681
that kids say
the darndest things.

00:26.716 --> 00:28.511
It's been scientifically
proven.

00:28.545 --> 00:30.961
Are you Apollo Gauntlet?

00:30.996 --> 00:32.170
Yeah?

00:32.204 --> 00:36.070
I have a message from
the Bellenus family...

00:37.416 --> 00:40.937
Whoa, man! Ever heard the term
"don't punch the messenger"?

00:40.971 --> 00:43.422
Come on, I've seen, like,
a million mob movies --

00:43.457 --> 00:44.906
dude comes up to you, says,

00:44.941 --> 00:46.943
"I got a message
from Mr. Moretti."

00:46.977 --> 00:49.118
Boom!
Shoots ya in the face.

00:49.152 --> 00:51.913
I know it's either that
or, "Mr. Moretti says hello!"

00:51.948 --> 00:52.638
Boom!

00:52.673 --> 00:54.606
Shoots you in the face.

00:54.640 --> 00:58.920
"Mr. Gauntlet --
you are formally invited

00:58.955 --> 01:00.715
to attend the annual

01:00.750 --> 01:03.097
Dinner of Diplomats
at Castle Bellenus."

01:03.132 --> 01:04.547
[ Laughter ]Ooh-hoo-hoo!

01:04.581 --> 01:06.721
Oh, and there's
a private letter

01:06.756 --> 01:08.620
from Daphne in here as well!

01:08.654 --> 01:10.967
Give me that!

01:11.001 --> 01:13.107
Apollo, I've heard rumors

01:13.142 --> 01:14.833
that one of
the attending diplomats

01:14.867 --> 01:17.146
may be planning to
assassinate the King.

01:17.180 --> 01:19.320
I'd feel much safer
if you were there.

01:19.355 --> 01:20.804
Yours, Daphne.

01:20.839 --> 01:23.738
P.S., be inconspicuous!

01:23.773 --> 01:25.499
All right, well,
I got a mission now,

01:25.533 --> 01:28.398
so catch you dudes later.
Bye!

01:28.433 --> 01:29.917
Aw, what about us,
matey?

01:29.951 --> 01:32.989
I could get a guard uniform
and go in undercover!

01:33.023 --> 01:34.749
I could be your plus one.

01:34.784 --> 01:36.820
Uh, you know,
that might not be...

01:36.855 --> 01:39.099
And I can be your eyes
on the inside!

01:39.133 --> 01:41.031
And Puff...
Puff can be your...

01:41.066 --> 01:42.447
-Eww.
-All right, all right!

01:42.481 --> 01:45.139
You guys can be involved
in the mission, but, uh...

01:45.174 --> 01:49.626
Just keep in mind
the key word is "subtlety."

01:51.801 --> 01:57.186
Heeeeeeeeeey guyyyyyyyys.

01:57.220 --> 01:59.740
♪♪

02:01.190 --> 02:05.332
♪ Here comes Apollo Gauntlet

02:07.334 --> 02:12.166
Yeah, I'm here, uh, for
the diplomatical event-ening

02:12.201 --> 02:14.203
that's happening here
tonight?

02:14.237 --> 02:17.309
Oh, Christ, I think
I stepped in troll shit.

02:17.344 --> 02:21.279
And this...and this is,
uh, my First Lady.

02:21.313 --> 02:23.626
[ Whispering ] L-Let's hope
she's not my last.

02:23.660 --> 02:25.179
[ Laughs ]

02:25.214 --> 02:27.733
Okay, thank you, sir.
Just make sure your carriage

02:27.768 --> 02:29.287
is parked in
the designated are--

02:29.321 --> 02:30.288
Aah!
[ Gasping ]

02:30.322 --> 02:31.220
What are you doing?

02:31.254 --> 02:32.290
We were in.

02:32.324 --> 02:34.015
I need to borrow
his guard outfit.

02:34.050 --> 02:35.845
Just cutting off the oxygen
to his brain for a bit.

02:35.879 --> 02:37.467
Oh, okay.

02:37.502 --> 02:40.746
Well, we know that that's never
had an adverse effect on anyone.

02:40.781 --> 02:42.231
[ Feedback ]Monty: Can you guys hear me?

02:42.265 --> 02:42.990
Ohh!

02:43.024 --> 02:44.336
We're still setting up

02:44.371 --> 02:45.648
the recon vehicle.

02:45.682 --> 02:48.927
Just wanted to make sure
we'd be able to communicate

02:48.961 --> 02:51.481
once you're inside the castle.
Over.

02:51.516 --> 02:52.827
Okay, uh...cool.

02:52.862 --> 02:54.484
Thanks, Monty.
I have to go now.

02:54.519 --> 02:58.108
I'm currently watching
Superknife murder someone.

02:58.143 --> 02:59.489
And...

02:59.524 --> 03:01.215
down like a newborn.

03:01.250 --> 03:06.358
If he's dead, I will testify
against you at the trial.

03:06.393 --> 03:08.188
[ Crowd murmuring ]

03:08.222 --> 03:15.333
[ Dishes, silverware clinking ]

03:15.367 --> 03:16.955
Miss? Wine?

03:16.989 --> 03:19.371
You bet I do!
Fill 'er up!

03:21.546 --> 03:25.135
Madam, this bottle of wine
is over 500 years old.

03:25.170 --> 03:26.551
Mm. [ Gulps ]

03:26.585 --> 03:27.690
Tastes okay to me.

03:27.724 --> 03:29.243
-Ugh...
-Hey, we're here

03:29.278 --> 03:32.695
to stop an assassination,
not guzzle expensive booze!

03:32.729 --> 03:34.800
What are you so
pent up about?!

03:34.835 --> 03:36.457
[ Trumpet plays off-key ]And now I present

03:36.492 --> 03:39.426
the much venerated hosts
of the party --

03:39.460 --> 03:41.048
King and Queen Bellenus,

03:41.082 --> 03:43.257
accompanied by Prince Orenthal

03:43.292 --> 03:46.812
and his lovely betrothed,
Daphne!

03:46.847 --> 03:49.056
I just don't want you
to embarrass me.

03:49.090 --> 03:51.438
I'm well aware of
your fixation with Daphne.

03:51.472 --> 03:55.304
But guess what -- you're just
a bumpkin like me

03:55.338 --> 03:59.169
and these blue-bloods will
smell it by a country mile.

03:59.204 --> 04:01.896
Well, thanks for
the "Hannibal lecture"

04:01.931 --> 04:03.312
about what a hayseed I am.

04:03.346 --> 04:06.556
But I happen to think that
Daphne is quite fond of me.

04:06.591 --> 04:08.386
Oh, hi!

04:08.420 --> 04:10.905
In your dreams, Podunk.

04:10.940 --> 04:11.906
[ Chomps ]

04:11.941 --> 04:12.976
Look at that.

04:13.011 --> 04:14.288
The Queen of Freedonia?

04:14.323 --> 04:16.290
That dress is scandalous,
I tell you.

04:16.325 --> 04:18.844
Flaunting her...
l-luscious...

04:18.879 --> 04:20.674
youthful...figure.

04:20.708 --> 04:21.847
It's a disgrace.

04:21.882 --> 04:23.090
[ Barks, growls ]

04:23.124 --> 04:24.816
That's just on
the screen, dummy.

04:24.850 --> 04:26.093
You talk a big game,

04:26.127 --> 04:27.853
but you wouldn't even know
what to do

04:27.888 --> 04:29.579
if you got your paws
on that.

04:29.614 --> 04:32.410
[ Whines ]

04:32.444 --> 04:37.000
So, uh, what nation are
you representing, exactly?

04:37.035 --> 04:39.279
I'm Queen of Freedonia.

04:39.313 --> 04:39.969
Mm-hmm.

04:40.003 --> 04:40.935
Ooh, puppy!

04:40.970 --> 04:42.316
[ Barking ]
Ooh!

04:42.351 --> 04:44.491
[ Barking ][ Snaps fingers ]

04:44.525 --> 04:48.322
What exactly is it that you do
in this kingdom, Mr. Gauntlet?

04:48.357 --> 04:51.118
Me? Well, no offense
to your police force,

04:51.152 --> 04:53.120
but I feel there's room for,
uh, you know,

04:53.154 --> 04:55.467
o-o-outside h-heroic parties

04:55.502 --> 04:57.055
to keep an eye on...
on the crimes?

04:57.089 --> 04:58.332
I hate to disagree,

04:58.367 --> 05:00.507
but I do believe we have
our borders covered,

05:00.541 --> 05:01.818
on allfronts.

05:01.853 --> 05:05.132
So, you seem to be
going over pretty well.

05:05.166 --> 05:06.444
Yeah, funny. Hilarious.

05:06.478 --> 05:09.136
No, no, I -- no,
I really think, uh, you know,

05:09.170 --> 05:11.449
the king seemed impressed,
uh, by your, uh,

05:11.483 --> 05:13.382
[ Chuckling ] your story
that you just told.Shut -- shut up. Shut up.

05:13.416 --> 05:14.728
Will you shut
the [bleep] up, please?

05:14.762 --> 05:17.006
[ Slurring ]
Okay, I'm goin' in.

05:17.040 --> 05:20.630
In where?The bag?
You can barely walk.

05:20.665 --> 05:22.356
Shh, hey, shh, shut up.

05:22.391 --> 05:24.634
[ Whispering loudly ]
Listen -- it's all an act.

05:24.669 --> 05:29.190
If I come across
as extremely intoxicated,

05:29.225 --> 05:32.193
nobody will suspect
I'm actually casing the joint

05:32.228 --> 05:34.886
for suspicious activity.

05:34.920 --> 05:36.922
-[ Groans ]
-Urgh, there she goes.

05:36.957 --> 05:38.165
-Ow!
-Hey!

05:38.199 --> 05:41.237
Yeah, this is great.
This is great.

05:41.271 --> 05:43.826
Hey, Superknife!
Wazzup, dude?

05:43.860 --> 05:45.172
-Hey.
-Hmm?

05:45.206 --> 05:46.518
Are you new here?

05:46.553 --> 05:48.486
No, I'm often here.
All the time, in fact.

05:48.520 --> 05:50.902
Yeah, guarding things
and making sure things

05:50.936 --> 05:52.041
are properly...guarded.

05:52.075 --> 05:53.836
You have a spare moment?

05:53.870 --> 05:56.390
[ Sultry ] I have a lock
I can't open.

05:56.425 --> 05:58.427
And where's it located,
miss?

05:58.461 --> 06:00.843
I'll show you
once we get there.

06:00.877 --> 06:02.914
You can probably handle it.

06:02.948 --> 06:04.398
If he leaves with her,

06:04.433 --> 06:08.091
this is an act of gross,
gross misconduct.

06:08.126 --> 06:10.853
[ Chuckling ]
Okay...where's this lock?

06:10.887 --> 06:14.615
And there it is!
At 19:00 hours,

06:14.650 --> 06:20.518
Superknife abandoned his post
due to suspicious innuendo.

06:20.552 --> 06:24.901
[ Folk music plays ]

06:26.558 --> 06:28.318
[ Whispers ]
Apollo, come with me.

06:28.353 --> 06:30.424
Oh, yeah!
This is...great.

06:30.459 --> 06:33.531
So, have you noticed
any unusual activity?

06:33.565 --> 06:36.775
No? Come on, do you --
do you really think

06:36.810 --> 06:38.708
there's
an assassination plot?

06:38.743 --> 06:40.330
What are you implying?

06:40.365 --> 06:42.954
Oh, I dunno, uh,
it did occur to me

06:42.988 --> 06:44.887
that this might all
just be a ploy

06:44.921 --> 06:46.716
so that you could
see me again.

06:46.751 --> 06:48.269
[ Chuckling ] Oh, okay.

06:48.304 --> 06:51.963
So, I purposefully invented
a scenario of political intrigue

06:51.997 --> 06:53.930
to attract you here, but,
in actuality,

06:53.965 --> 06:55.898
my true intent was to
"see you again"?

06:55.932 --> 07:00.558
Well, O-Occam's Razor
dictates that, uh...yeah.

07:00.592 --> 07:03.664
Maybe you're not the hero
I thought you were.

07:03.699 --> 07:05.148
Then if I am not, uh,

07:05.183 --> 07:08.013
perhaps we have reached
an impasse on this eve,

07:08.048 --> 07:10.844
milady,
and I bid you adieu.

07:10.878 --> 07:11.845
Ow!

07:11.879 --> 07:13.467
[ All gasp ]Oh, no!

07:13.502 --> 07:14.848
It's gonna go,
it's gonna go!

07:14.882 --> 07:16.608
Oh, no, oh, no, it's going.

07:16.643 --> 07:18.645
Oh, no, it's gonna go.

07:18.679 --> 07:21.510
Whew! That was a close one.

07:22.476 --> 07:23.995
[ All gasp ]

07:24.029 --> 07:27.654
It was going to...melt...
anyway, so...

07:28.517 --> 07:30.760
[ Grunts ] Ow!

07:30.795 --> 07:33.142
Urgh! Ow!

07:33.901 --> 07:35.627
Ohh, whoa.

07:35.662 --> 07:36.870
What's this?

07:36.904 --> 07:38.665
An invisibility cloak?

07:38.699 --> 07:42.945
Now let's see what's
going on in the kitchen.

07:42.979 --> 07:44.774
[ Twinkle! ]

07:44.809 --> 07:46.051
Urgh! Ow!

07:46.086 --> 07:47.639
[ Grumbles ]

07:47.674 --> 07:50.366
Ohh.
Hello, sweeties.

07:50.400 --> 07:53.369
[ Chuckles, munching ]

07:53.403 --> 07:56.993
Death to the ruling class,
my brothers and sisters.

07:57.028 --> 07:58.374
-And in mere moments...
-Huh?

07:58.408 --> 08:00.134
...you will deliver it
to them

08:00.169 --> 08:02.171
on a silver platter.
[ Laughs ]

08:02.205 --> 08:04.484
Yup-yah! Yup-yah!Yup-yah! Yup-yah!

08:08.004 --> 08:09.489
Apollo! Emergency!

08:09.523 --> 08:10.490
[ Feedback ]

08:10.524 --> 08:11.974
[ Grunts ]

08:12.008 --> 08:14.079
Okay, we're in
a pickle now.

08:14.114 --> 08:15.978
I've lost communication
with Apollo,

08:16.012 --> 08:19.084
so one of you needs to tell him
the cake is poisoned!

08:19.119 --> 08:20.258
-Pronto, people!
-[ Gasps ]

08:20.292 --> 08:23.019
Hey, come back here!

08:25.090 --> 08:27.576
Rubis:
Ow, urgh, ow, oh!

08:28.128 --> 08:30.820
Ahh!

08:30.855 --> 08:32.926
[ Rubis panting ]

08:32.960 --> 08:35.273
[ Slurring ]
The cake is poisoned.

08:35.307 --> 08:37.724
The lake is f-frozen?

08:37.758 --> 08:39.173
The cake is poisoned!

08:39.208 --> 08:41.279
The steak...is...overdone?

08:41.313 --> 08:43.005
The cake is poisoned!

08:43.039 --> 08:44.420
The...drapes are chosen.

08:44.454 --> 08:47.285
[ Yelling ] Aw, crikey,
the cake is poisoned!

08:47.319 --> 08:48.597
Huh?![ All gasp ]

08:52.601 --> 08:54.568
It's time to clear the table!

08:54.603 --> 08:55.293
[ All gasp ]

08:55.327 --> 08:56.846
And this one, too!

08:56.881 --> 08:57.709
[ All gasp ]

08:57.744 --> 08:59.228
Now the question is --

08:59.262 --> 09:01.955
who poisoned the cake?

09:01.989 --> 09:03.266
[ Approaching footsteps ]

09:03.922 --> 09:06.407
This is not a cake-off,
this is not a bake-off --

09:06.442 --> 09:09.376
no, this is a full-on brawl!

09:09.410 --> 09:12.862
The secret ingredient tonight
is violence.

09:12.897 --> 09:15.831
Ooh, right in the entrees!

09:17.108 --> 09:17.936
[ Groans ]

09:17.971 --> 09:20.076
[ All gasp ]

09:21.595 --> 09:24.633
[ Applause ]

09:24.667 --> 09:25.495
Oh, shut up,

09:25.530 --> 09:27.394
I don't need your applause,

09:27.428 --> 09:30.604
you boring, inbred elitists.

09:30.639 --> 09:31.743
You sicken me.

09:31.778 --> 09:32.779
But you know what?

09:32.813 --> 09:34.574
Even with this experience today,

09:34.608 --> 09:37.300
I will continue my efforts
to protect you.

09:37.335 --> 09:40.234
Why?
Because I'm stupid like that.

09:40.269 --> 09:43.341
Because I am attempting
in my own small way

09:43.375 --> 09:47.138
to maintain sanity
amidst all this madness.

09:47.172 --> 09:48.933
Thanks, Apollo.

09:48.967 --> 09:50.590
♪♪

09:50.624 --> 09:52.730
[ Gasps ]
Guards, eject him!

09:52.764 --> 09:54.076
[ Record scratch ]

09:54.110 --> 09:57.976
[ As Daniel Plainview ]
I am the Third Revelation!

09:58.011 --> 09:59.288
♪♪

09:59.322 --> 10:01.152
Congratulations, everyone.

10:01.186 --> 10:02.774
Mission accomplished.

10:02.809 --> 10:04.293
Ah, the best part, I say,

10:04.327 --> 10:06.847
is we're really making
headway as a team.

10:06.882 --> 10:09.781
Yes! And it can feel like
a Boys' Club with you guys

10:09.816 --> 10:13.129
at times, but you finally let
me pull my weight on this one.

10:13.164 --> 10:14.268
[ Barks ]

10:14.303 --> 10:17.133
Yeah, yeah, yes,
it was amazing.

10:17.168 --> 10:18.618
Not since Seal Team Six

10:18.652 --> 10:21.759
has an operation been
pulled off so smoothly.

10:21.793 --> 10:24.485
I got to say it --
I'm proud of you, Apollo.

10:24.520 --> 10:25.141
Yeah?

10:25.176 --> 10:26.626
Takes a lot of balls

10:26.660 --> 10:28.282
to wear that outfit
in public.

10:28.317 --> 10:29.629
[ Laughter ]

10:29.663 --> 10:33.287
And with no apparent
hint of embarrassment.

10:33.322 --> 10:35.117
Yeah, it's pretty lame, bro.

10:35.151 --> 10:37.671
That's it. I'm taking
your allowance away.

10:37.706 --> 10:39.811
[ Boing! ]

10:39.846 --> 10:42.503
♪♪
